WEBVTT

00:03:01.222 --> 00:03:02.849
(Gi Haneul.)

00:03:03.558 --> 00:03:04.100
Gi Haneul!

00:03:09.147 --> 00:03:10.106
Are you okay?

00:03:10.815 --> 00:03:11.691
What happened?

00:03:11.816 --> 00:03:13.318
Did you have a bad dream?

00:03:14.152 --> 00:03:15.361
What... a dream?

00:03:16.196 --> 00:03:17.864
That's ridiculous. I...

00:03:17.864 --> 00:03:19.776
I'm someone who never dreams, you know.

00:03:19.776 --> 00:03:20.491
Got that?

00:03:21.034 --> 00:03:23.244
What do you know?
You don't know anything.

00:03:23.286 --> 00:03:24.287
What, you think...

00:03:24.412 --> 00:03:25.872
I dreamed about you or something?

00:03:26.122 --> 00:03:26.789
Unbelievable.

00:03:28.791 --> 00:03:30.543
Are you feeling unwell?

00:03:31.211 --> 00:03:32.754
Your face is really red.

00:03:34.714 --> 00:03:36.132
You look like you have a fever.

00:03:38.593 --> 00:03:39.594
Not at all.

00:03:40.470 --> 00:03:43.431
Fever? What fever?
What do you know? This is ridiculous.

00:04:05.703 --> 00:04:08.581
(Huh, this feeling of familiarity?)

00:04:08.623 --> 00:04:09.916
(I kind of like it?)

00:04:09.916 --> 00:04:10.625
Feeling good?

00:04:16.631 --> 00:04:17.840
Shall I go in?

00:04:41.239 --> 00:04:42.949
Haneul, did you remember?

00:04:43.116 --> 00:04:43.616
No!

00:04:48.371 --> 00:04:49.289
Haneul.

00:04:50.581 --> 00:04:51.291
What?

00:04:52.583 --> 00:04:53.293
Thank you.

00:04:54.961 --> 00:04:55.795
For what?

00:04:57.171 --> 00:04:58.131
For believing me.

00:05:02.302 --> 00:05:04.304
You're part of the problem too.

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:06.202
What kind of behavior did you have

00:05:06.202 --> 00:05:07.682
to get rumors like this going around?

00:05:07.682 --> 00:05:08.516
That's not it.

00:05:08.516 --> 00:05:09.952
What do you mean, 'that's not it'?

00:05:10.852 --> 00:05:11.728
Could it be that...

00:05:12.937 --> 00:05:14.063
you think I'm just a fake?

00:05:14.480 --> 00:05:16.107
You know I have no one else but you.

00:05:17.066 --> 00:05:18.192
I know that,

00:05:18.624 --> 00:05:20.236
but it seems you get confused sometimes.

00:05:21.904 --> 00:05:22.989
I'll be watching.

00:05:23.781 --> 00:05:24.866
From now on.

00:05:25.033 --> 00:05:26.034
Watch your behavior.

00:05:26.528 --> 00:05:27.535
Be careful around women.

00:05:28.411 --> 00:05:29.329
Got it?

00:05:33.333 --> 00:05:34.208
Hmm.

00:05:43.718 --> 00:05:44.427
Gi Haneul.

00:05:47.430 --> 00:05:47.930
Get sleep.

00:05:50.683 --> 00:05:52.101
What am I to you?

00:05:54.688 --> 00:05:55.768
What are you talking about?

00:06:01.027 --> 00:06:03.821
What kind of Yeo Saebyeok
am I to you right now?

00:06:04.614 --> 00:06:06.908
Am I nineteen or twenty-nine?

00:06:08.659 --> 00:06:09.994
Why does that matter?

00:06:11.120 --> 00:06:12.663
You're still the same Yeo Saebyeok.

00:06:13.956 --> 00:06:14.957
By any chance,

00:06:15.917 --> 00:06:18.294
do you remember more about us?

00:06:19.504 --> 00:06:21.255
Is that why you took my side?

00:06:22.548 --> 00:06:23.383
It's just...

00:06:25.510 --> 00:06:27.929
you're a good person.

00:06:28.721 --> 00:06:29.472
You

00:06:30.500 --> 00:06:32.300
shouldn't have to go through
rumors like that.

00:06:35.728 --> 00:06:36.979
But you don't like me.

00:06:40.858 --> 00:06:42.151
It's not that I didn't like you.

00:06:42.443 --> 00:06:44.153
I just didn't realize I liked you.

00:06:47.949 --> 00:06:48.699
What about now?

00:06:53.204 --> 00:06:55.373
I don't know... This is so frustrating.

00:06:59.210 --> 00:07:01.462
I'm glad you're here.

00:07:03.506 --> 00:07:05.550
Stay with me from now on too.

00:07:09.762 --> 00:07:10.596
Hmm.

00:08:03.774 --> 00:08:10.124
=Never Forget Your Enemy=

00:08:11.157 --> 00:08:15.244
=Episode 5=
(Day)

00:08:27.757 --> 00:08:28.841
You remember?

00:08:30.176 --> 00:08:31.093
Looks like I do.

00:08:38.184 --> 00:08:39.227
Actually,

00:08:41.521 --> 00:08:43.731
when I said I was quitting tennis,

00:08:45.775 --> 00:08:48.069
a part of me thought
that might really happen.

00:08:52.949 --> 00:08:54.528
Even after doing sports my whole life,

00:08:54.951 --> 00:08:56.911
I was always afraid of the next match.

00:08:58.454 --> 00:08:59.622
Even if I win today,

00:09:00.414 --> 00:09:02.625
I might get eliminated
in the qualifiers tomorrow.

00:09:06.087 --> 00:09:07.630
Why is losing so scary?

00:09:10.550 --> 00:09:11.676
I'm scared too.

00:09:12.260 --> 00:09:13.135
But...

00:09:15.137 --> 00:09:16.389
I want to keep going.

00:09:17.139 --> 00:09:18.057
Then do it.

00:09:18.224 --> 00:09:19.642
No need to hesitate.

00:09:22.645 --> 00:09:23.604
I don't know.

00:09:27.942 --> 00:09:28.734
Do you

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:30.695
believe in yourself?

00:09:31.612 --> 00:09:32.154
I...

00:09:33.155 --> 00:09:34.073
believe in you too.

00:09:48.004 --> 00:09:48.838
Have a safe trip.

00:09:51.257 --> 00:09:53.175
Oh, right. Yeo Saebyeok.

00:09:53.926 --> 00:09:54.677
What?

00:09:55.219 --> 00:09:58.014
I... remember something.

00:10:05.438 --> 00:10:07.565
You started it first! So be ready!

00:10:07.642 --> 00:10:09.148
Oh, please.

00:10:22.426 --> 00:10:24.332
(Coach)

00:10:28.252 --> 00:10:29.128
Hello.

00:10:29.503 --> 00:10:31.104
It's been a while since I contacted you.

00:10:39.555 --> 00:10:40.848
Why are you spacing out?

00:10:41.974 --> 00:10:43.476
I'm exhausted.

00:10:44.235 --> 00:10:46.395
I wish all the companies around here
would go bankrupt.

00:10:47.063 --> 00:10:49.065
Do office workers die
if they don't drink coffee?

00:10:49.190 --> 00:10:50.483
They say it's like an IV drip.

00:10:52.777 --> 00:10:54.320
I saw the article.

00:10:55.529 --> 00:10:56.197
Article?

00:10:56.864 --> 00:10:57.907
Saebyeok's scandal.

00:10:58.574 --> 00:11:00.576
They said the photos
were all manipulated.

00:11:00.910 --> 00:11:03.371
Someone even posted
an apology saying they did it.

00:11:04.538 --> 00:11:05.164
Really?

00:11:08.256 --> 00:11:10.016
Looks like someone else
got sacrificed again.

00:11:10.711 --> 00:11:11.462
What a shame.

00:11:12.254 --> 00:11:12.838
What is?

00:11:13.422 --> 00:11:15.549
If they were actually a thing,

00:11:16.133 --> 00:11:18.010
I was going to confess to you.

00:11:18.969 --> 00:11:20.680
You thought I'd accept, huh?

00:11:21.472 --> 00:11:22.515
Am I not your type?

00:11:26.519 --> 00:11:27.311
I'm...

00:11:27.936 --> 00:11:29.280
thinking of playing tennis again.

00:11:29.647 --> 00:11:30.815
Tennis?

00:11:32.983 --> 00:11:33.776
Well,

00:11:34.402 --> 00:11:35.778
I don't have a clear plan.

00:11:36.570 --> 00:11:37.488
All of a sudden?

00:11:38.739 --> 00:11:40.282
Because I feel like I'll regret it

00:11:40.908 --> 00:11:42.144
if I keep living the same way.

00:11:43.119 --> 00:11:43.744
Why?

00:11:45.329 --> 00:11:47.164
So far, I've only blamed others

00:11:47.832 --> 00:11:49.750
and just run away,
acting like the victim.

00:11:51.419 --> 00:11:51.961
If I keep

00:11:52.294 --> 00:11:53.462
running away,

00:11:54.046 --> 00:11:55.648
I'm afraid I won't be able to come back.

00:11:57.425 --> 00:11:58.259
Actually,

00:11:59.301 --> 00:12:01.262
what I wanted most was tennis.

00:12:01.554 --> 00:12:02.972
So what if you can't come back?

00:12:03.472 --> 00:12:05.224
You can just take a new path.

00:12:06.767 --> 00:12:08.544
But I've left

00:12:08.544 --> 00:12:09.937
too much behind.

00:12:10.813 --> 00:12:12.148
Like Saebyeok?

00:12:12.857 --> 00:12:14.734
Well... Saebyeok,

00:12:15.067 --> 00:12:16.402
my family,

00:12:17.236 --> 00:12:18.446
and friends.

00:12:19.947 --> 00:12:20.948
I'm jealous.

00:12:22.575 --> 00:12:23.492
And you too.

00:12:28.247 --> 00:12:29.248
That's cool.

00:12:30.541 --> 00:12:31.625
I'll cheer for you.

00:12:32.126 --> 00:12:32.918
Thanks.

00:12:37.882 --> 00:12:39.550
(Dummy)

00:12:39.550 --> 00:12:40.217
Hold on.

00:12:45.264 --> 00:12:45.806
Hello?

00:12:46.140 --> 00:12:46.720
Where are you?

00:12:47.391 --> 00:12:48.017
Why?

00:12:48.434 --> 00:12:49.280
Because I missed you.

00:12:50.016 --> 00:12:50.686
I'm hanging up.

00:12:50.686 --> 00:12:52.246
There's a place we need to go together.

00:12:54.064 --> 00:12:54.690
Where?

00:12:54.880 --> 00:12:56.080
You'll know when we get there.

00:12:59.898 --> 00:13:03.264
(Hankook High School)

00:13:10.915 --> 00:13:11.916
Why the school?

00:13:12.917 --> 00:13:13.751
Just follow me.

00:13:32.394 --> 00:13:33.103
Let's go.

00:13:33.896 --> 00:13:35.022
He's waiting.

00:13:41.904 --> 00:13:44.365
Eyes, eyes, watch your eyes.

00:13:44.615 --> 00:13:45.449
A little more.

00:13:53.624 --> 00:13:54.458
Hold on.

00:13:55.751 --> 00:13:56.460
Going!

00:13:56.794 --> 00:13:58.080
Yes, just a little. A little.

00:13:58.963 --> 00:13:59.797
That's it.

00:13:59.964 --> 00:14:01.215
Okay, one more time!

00:14:02.508 --> 00:14:04.510
Oh, hey, let's do two more.

00:14:13.060 --> 00:14:13.936
Gi Haneul.

00:14:15.688 --> 00:14:16.647
Hey, you.

00:14:17.314 --> 00:14:18.983
Are you really going to quit like this?

00:14:25.920 --> 00:14:26.907
Rehabilitation.

00:14:27.072 --> 00:14:27.968
You can just do rehab.

00:14:27.968 --> 00:14:29.118
Even if I do rehab,

00:14:29.410 --> 00:14:30.619
what would change?

00:14:31.036 --> 00:14:31.912
Didn't you hear?

00:14:32.580 --> 00:14:33.664
They said even with rehab,

00:14:33.956 --> 00:14:36.208
there's no guarantee
I can continue as a player.

00:14:36.500 --> 00:14:38.335
Let's try. How will you
know if you don't try?

00:14:38.335 --> 00:14:39.253
How could I not know?

00:14:40.087 --> 00:14:41.547
Everyone in the world knows.

00:14:41.714 --> 00:14:43.132
Tennis player Gi Haneul is injured.

00:14:43.674 --> 00:14:45.092
Playing career uncertain.

00:14:46.594 --> 00:14:48.929
It's all over the news,
and how could I not know?

00:14:50.598 --> 00:14:52.975
They say it's a miracle
that I can even walk.

00:15:03.861 --> 00:15:05.446
I won't play tennis again.

00:15:28.427 --> 00:15:30.429
I really want to play tennis...

00:15:48.948 --> 00:15:51.909
(I kept hearing about you
through Saebyeok.)

00:15:55.329 --> 00:15:56.163
Really?

00:15:56.622 --> 00:15:57.498
Yeah.

00:15:58.165 --> 00:16:00.960
Do you still bicker
with Saebyeok these days?

00:16:01.418 --> 00:16:02.920
That's all we do, bicker.

00:16:03.587 --> 00:16:04.505
You two

00:16:04.755 --> 00:16:07.132
haven't changed,
whether you're nineteen or twenty-nine.

00:16:08.467 --> 00:16:10.010
I'm still nineteen at heart.

00:16:10.344 --> 00:16:11.261
That's nice.

00:16:12.805 --> 00:16:13.305
So,

00:16:13.889 --> 00:16:15.391
what brings you two here today?

00:16:18.769 --> 00:16:21.397
I want to try playing tennis again.

00:16:22.606 --> 00:16:23.524
Really?

00:16:25.234 --> 00:16:26.986
I'm not dreaming of being a pro again.

00:16:27.361 --> 00:16:29.071
I just want to

00:16:29.613 --> 00:16:31.532
hold a racket again.

00:16:32.116 --> 00:16:33.117
That was a good call.

00:16:33.617 --> 00:16:34.576
A really good call.

00:16:36.620 --> 00:16:38.080
I've only thought about it so far.

00:16:41.792 --> 00:16:42.918
Then,

00:16:43.711 --> 00:16:47.339
could you come by on weekends
when you have time and keep helping out?

00:16:47.548 --> 00:16:48.298
Me?

00:16:49.008 --> 00:16:50.801
There's no better teacher than you.

00:16:51.260 --> 00:16:54.221
You know better than anyone
what's hard right now

00:16:54.596 --> 00:16:56.056
and what's needed, Haneul.

00:16:57.266 --> 00:16:59.168
Teach the kids this and that,

00:16:59.168 --> 00:17:01.228
and practice tennis yourself
whenever you have time.

00:17:04.898 --> 00:17:06.275
I'll think about it.

00:17:11.613 --> 00:17:14.116
What do you think about
what the coach said?

00:17:15.492 --> 00:17:16.785
It's sudden,

00:17:17.152 --> 00:17:18.656
but it seems like a good opportunity.

00:17:19.163 --> 00:17:20.539
Think it through.

00:17:21.984 --> 00:17:23.296
Getting to meet the coach...

00:17:23.296 --> 00:17:24.096
Grateful?

00:17:26.045 --> 00:17:26.837
Cute.

00:17:29.048 --> 00:17:30.466
You're quitting the cafe, right?

00:17:31.133 --> 00:17:32.009
I guess so.

00:17:32.593 --> 00:17:34.803
But if I quit,
Junghan will have a hard time alone.

00:17:34.887 --> 00:17:36.388
Why do you care about that?

00:17:37.181 --> 00:17:38.474
He will figure it out.

00:17:38.891 --> 00:17:39.725
Really?

00:17:40.350 --> 00:17:41.477
Let's go home and eat.

00:17:41.977 --> 00:17:42.978
What's for side dishes?

00:17:43.729 --> 00:17:44.271
Frog dishes.

00:17:45.230 --> 00:17:46.315
Protein.

00:17:52.404 --> 00:17:52.863
Haneul.

00:17:53.489 --> 00:17:53.989
Hmm?

00:17:55.240 --> 00:17:55.616
Why?

00:17:58.202 --> 00:17:58.869
This.

00:18:04.458 --> 00:18:05.042
This is...

00:18:05.542 --> 00:18:08.253
(Gi Haneul)
I always thought you'd play tennis again.

00:18:12.591 --> 00:18:14.176
Don't worry about anything.

00:18:14.336 --> 00:18:15.392
Just think about yourself.

00:18:20.140 --> 00:18:21.975
This is probably why I liked you.

00:18:24.686 --> 00:18:25.395
Haneul.

00:18:30.016 --> 00:18:31.712
I won't let you get away
with this today!

00:18:36.365 --> 00:18:38.867
It's perfect now,
but just follow through

00:18:38.951 --> 00:18:41.248
a bit more on your swing,
and make contact in front.

00:18:41.248 --> 00:18:41.888
Okay.

00:18:41.888 --> 00:18:44.608
Next, without opening up too much,
just bend your knees a little.

00:18:44.608 --> 00:18:45.536
Want to give it a try?

00:18:46.458 --> 00:18:48.043
Nice! One more time.

00:18:48.919 --> 00:18:51.213
Okay!

00:19:01.723 --> 00:19:02.766
(Doing okay?)

00:19:03.424 --> 00:19:04.736
(Don't push yourself too hard.)

00:19:06.061 --> 00:19:07.104
(Did you eat?)

00:19:08.397 --> 00:19:09.481
(See you at home later.)

00:19:11.104 --> 00:19:12.512
(How about chicken and beer today?)

00:19:13.235 --> 00:19:15.279
(Okay, I'm home!)

00:19:32.670 --> 00:19:33.630
What are you doing here?

00:19:35.299 --> 00:19:36.717
Is Haneul not home?

00:19:36.864 --> 00:19:38.051
Why are you looking for him?

00:19:38.719 --> 00:19:40.888
He left some stuff at the cafe.

00:19:42.347 --> 00:19:43.182
Just throw it away.

00:19:43.557 --> 00:19:44.266
No.

00:19:45.726 --> 00:19:47.477
I'll give it to him when I see him.

00:19:55.319 --> 00:19:56.278
You,

00:19:56.278 --> 00:19:57.613
don't hang around Haneul.

00:19:59.740 --> 00:20:01.116
I like Haneul.

00:20:02.576 --> 00:20:04.286
So I'm going to have him.

00:20:05.344 --> 00:20:07.080
How could someone like you
possibly do that?

00:20:07.456 --> 00:20:08.415
I'll just

00:20:09.249 --> 00:20:09.833
do it well.

00:20:11.001 --> 00:20:12.669
I have a bit of faith in myself.

00:20:15.339 --> 00:20:16.840
Try it. See if it works.

00:20:19.301 --> 00:20:19.927
Yes.

00:20:20.594 --> 00:20:21.720
Please root for me.

00:20:22.387 --> 00:20:23.764
You too, good luck.

00:20:49.581 --> 00:20:50.415
No.

00:20:50.999 --> 00:20:51.583
Why?

00:20:51.792 --> 00:20:52.542
Just one sip.

00:20:52.876 --> 00:20:53.877
My throat's dry.

00:20:55.963 --> 00:20:57.005
I can't even speak.

00:20:57.422 --> 00:20:59.466
That's why you shouldn't
overwork your ankle.

00:21:00.133 --> 00:21:01.635
Right now... you're

00:21:02.052 --> 00:21:03.929
overworking my throat too.

00:21:04.224 --> 00:21:05.088
Don't be ridiculous.

00:21:06.144 --> 00:21:08.225
Maybe you should grease
your throat with chicken.

00:21:11.186 --> 00:21:12.479
This isn't working.

00:22:47.520 --> 00:22:49.088
Oh, right.

00:22:49.338 --> 00:22:50.432
(It's Dummy's birthday. Happy birthday!)

00:22:57.626 --> 00:22:58.877
What should I get him?

00:22:59.200 --> 00:23:00.736
He already has pretty much everything.

00:23:04.026 --> 00:23:07.136
(Yeo Saebyeok)

00:23:07.511 --> 00:23:08.553
(Yeo Saebyeok)
A 100-question list?

00:23:10.806 --> 00:23:14.434
Favorite foods... Chicken, pizza,

00:23:14.643 --> 00:23:15.852
bossam.

00:23:17.020 --> 00:23:17.979
Nothing's changed.

00:23:19.439 --> 00:23:21.056
Favorite color?

00:23:21.056 --> 00:23:22.109
(My favorite color: Sky blue)

00:23:22.109 --> 00:23:23.193
Sky blue.

00:23:25.904 --> 00:23:27.364
Ah, jeez...

00:23:34.704 --> 00:23:36.915
If you keep pulling your hair
like that, you'll go bald.

00:23:40.919 --> 00:23:42.546
I can't think of anything.

00:23:43.713 --> 00:23:45.424
What idea?

00:23:45.882 --> 00:23:47.551
It's Saebyeok's birthday today.

00:23:47.801 --> 00:23:49.472
I don't know what to get him
as a present.

00:23:49.920 --> 00:23:52.639
Oh, it's Saebyeok's birthday.

00:23:52.736 --> 00:23:53.856
I thought...

00:23:56.435 --> 00:23:57.561
Got any ideas?

00:23:59.020 --> 00:23:59.688
Well...

00:24:00.240 --> 00:24:02.120
He's such a star,
so he probably has everything.

00:24:02.368 --> 00:24:04.032
That's exactly what I'm saying.

00:24:05.360 --> 00:24:07.404
That's when sincerity matters most.

00:24:07.946 --> 00:24:08.738
Sincerity?

00:24:09.573 --> 00:24:12.701
How about you prepare
a birthday meal yourself?

00:24:14.327 --> 00:24:15.328
I can't cook.

00:24:15.620 --> 00:24:18.039
Is cooking skill the issue?
It's the thought that counts.

00:24:21.001 --> 00:24:23.336
Okay... Got it!

00:24:23.545 --> 00:24:25.422
Oh, that's a good idea.

00:24:25.589 --> 00:24:26.631
Thanks for the compliment.

00:24:30.927 --> 00:24:31.761
(Haneul.)

00:24:32.220 --> 00:24:34.347
(I never expected that anyway.)

00:24:38.852 --> 00:24:40.061
Gi Haneul.

00:24:43.488 --> 00:24:45.030
When was that?

00:24:49.029 --> 00:24:50.572
Why toss the gift like that?

00:24:52.157 --> 00:24:53.241
Gi Haneul...

00:24:53.909 --> 00:24:55.327
Kind of a bad boy move, huh?

00:25:01.249 --> 00:25:03.168
I should go grocery shopping first.

00:25:03.936 --> 00:25:04.920
You're leaving already?

00:25:05.837 --> 00:25:06.838
I've got shopping to do.

00:25:07.380 --> 00:25:08.131
So busy.

00:25:08.465 --> 00:25:10.050
Then when do we meet again?

00:25:10.592 --> 00:25:11.384
Us?

00:25:12.032 --> 00:25:12.480
Well...

00:25:12.768 --> 00:25:14.513
We'll probably see each other
again someday.

00:25:15.222 --> 00:25:16.473
Anyway, I'm leaving!

00:25:17.728 --> 00:25:18.688
What do I need to do?

00:25:19.851 --> 00:25:20.560
Seaweed soup.

00:25:36.320 --> 00:25:37.244
Ah, this is hard.

00:25:40.800 --> 00:25:42.165
But even I think I did well.

00:26:19.286 --> 00:26:20.203
Thank you!

00:26:20.704 --> 00:26:21.913
Thank you.

00:26:27.752 --> 00:26:28.670
Good work!

00:26:28.795 --> 00:26:29.984
Thank you for your hard work!

00:26:37.095 --> 00:26:38.930
Thank you, have a good day!

00:26:38.930 --> 00:26:39.723
Happy birthday.

00:26:41.641 --> 00:26:44.394
- Good work.
- Happy birthday.

00:26:47.856 --> 00:26:48.982
(Drive safe.)

00:26:49.399 --> 00:26:51.192
Call me if anything happens.

00:26:52.736 --> 00:26:53.403
Thanks.

00:26:54.321 --> 00:26:54.696
Go.

00:27:19.429 --> 00:27:21.056
Okay...

00:27:41.201 --> 00:27:42.702
I didn't order anything else.

00:27:53.088 --> 00:27:55.465
Did Yeo Saebyeok call you two
over saying it's his birthday?

00:27:56.257 --> 00:27:57.133
He's such a kid.

00:27:58.802 --> 00:28:00.553
It's Saebyeok's birthday today, right?

00:28:00.640 --> 00:28:01.888
Give it here. I'll carry it.

00:28:07.227 --> 00:28:07.894
What's this?

00:28:08.061 --> 00:28:09.479
Alcohol? Sake?

00:28:10.063 --> 00:28:11.106
Ah, well...

00:28:15.819 --> 00:28:16.861
Weren't you all here

00:28:17.112 --> 00:28:18.822
for a birthday party?

00:28:19.072 --> 00:28:19.864
Haneul.

00:28:21.408 --> 00:28:22.450
Actually,

00:28:22.867 --> 00:28:23.785
today...

00:28:52.564 --> 00:28:53.773
Don't turn it on.

00:28:54.733 --> 00:28:55.525
Gi Haneul?

00:29:00.947 --> 00:29:02.282
What are you?

00:29:36.954 --> 00:29:39.991
♪The more I try to run away♪

00:29:40.289 --> 00:29:41.972
♪The clearer it becomes♪

00:29:43.574 --> 00:29:46.864
♪Even the word "love"♪

00:29:47.160 --> 00:29:48.351
♪Can't convey how I feel♪

00:29:50.420 --> 00:29:53.493
♪Watching your shadow moving forward♪

00:29:53.722 --> 00:29:55.354
♪Sometimes, I resent you♪

00:29:55.354 --> 00:29:57.216
♪But without you,
everything feels strange♪

00:29:57.445 --> 00:30:02.515
♪The pain also makes me grow♪

00:30:03.962 --> 00:30:05.862
♪There is a lot to say♪

00:30:05.862 --> 00:30:07.282
♪Trying to separate us♪

00:30:07.595 --> 00:30:10.440
♪Even if I look like a fool♪

00:30:11.036 --> 00:30:12.556
♪It doesn't matter♪

00:30:12.556 --> 00:30:14.522
♪This is how we are♪

00:30:14.522 --> 00:30:17.437
♪Connected to each other♪

00:30:17.498 --> 00:30:21.017
♪We are truly strange♪

00:30:21.498 --> 00:30:24.549
♪Pushing each other away,
yet embracing again♪

00:30:24.549 --> 00:30:26.842
♪Between love and pain♪

00:30:26.874 --> 00:30:29.885
♪In some corner♪

00:30:30.036 --> 00:30:33.521
♪In the end, we can only be together♪

00:30:40.628 --> 00:30:44.460
♪Because that's us♪

00:30:47.914 --> 00:30:49.274
♪Even if what we said yesterday♪

00:30:49.274 --> 00:30:50.728
♪Remains in the heart♪

00:30:50.906 --> 00:30:52.698
♪As time passes♪

00:30:52.698 --> 00:30:53.914
♪Maybe I'll laugh about it♪

00:30:53.914 --> 00:30:55.994
♪Even those painful memories♪

00:30:55.994 --> 00:30:57.114
♪Are also ours♪

00:30:57.268 --> 00:30:59.848
♪Seems we can♪

00:30:59.848 --> 00:31:01.785
♪Be more understanding♪

00:31:02.260 --> 00:31:04.444
♪I clearly told myself♪

00:31:05.466 --> 00:31:07.724
♪Never to see you again♪

00:31:07.962 --> 00:31:10.671
♪But hearing your voice♪

00:31:11.028 --> 00:31:12.058
♪I completely break down♪